# S06-T09: Enterprise README

## Objective
Author repo README presenting the project as "Realtime Frontend Systems Engineer" portfolio for DefTech vacancy.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Sections (mandatory):
  - Architecture Overview (with diagrams)
  - Rendering Pipeline (scheduler, OffscreenCanvas, Workers)
  - Performance Strategy (adaptive quality, frame budgets)
  - Telemetry Pipeline (binary protocol, Workers, buffers)
  - Video Pipeline (Camera API, WebRTC, RTSP, source switching)
  - Embedded Deployment (Tauri 2, Raspberry Pi 5, kiosk mode)
  - Runtime Modes (Browser / PWA / Tauri)
  - Touch UX Strategy
  - Testing Strategy (unit, component, E2E, stress)
  - Screenshots / demo video links
- Inline diagrams (Mermaid) for architecture & telemetry pipeline.
- Positioning paragraph (top): "Realtime Frontend Systems Engineer".

## Steps
1. Outline README skeleton.
2. Draft architecture overview + Mermaid diagram.
3. Fill pipeline sections referencing sprint outputs.
4. Add screenshots placeholder + final positioning paragraph.

## Invariants
- No marketing fluff — engineering tone, specific decisions.
- Every section references concrete files/modules in repo.
- Diagrams render in GitHub markdown.
